  .mdl-card__supporting-text
    p
      | By trade, I'm a Software Engineer at&nbsp;
      a(href='https://bn.co') Brand Networks
      | .
      | I've worked on projects both big and small&mdash;some spending millions of dollars buying ads on social channels like Facebook and Twitter.
      | My goal is to be the mystical "10x engineer" by developing tools and processes that turn 10 1x engineers into 2x engineers.
    p
      | Most of my spare time is filled with learning new technologies to assist me in my work.
      | Recent efforts have centered around highly scalable and available distributed systems using Ansible, Docker, and etcd to name a few.
      | Beyond that, I've begun researching Apache Spark to process increasingly large data sets originating from medical, IoT, and the data originating from modern distributed systems.
