      | Lastly, while building software and infrastructure is fun, sometimes I need to build something I can hold.
      | To satisfy this desire, I've set up a small woodshop in my basement.
      | One nice side effect of this is that I can build what I want for less than I'd probably pay for it.
      | If only software always worked that way.
